data.description: Gorgeous 3 bed,2 bath,2 garage home!!! Nestled in a meticulously maintained, deed-restricted community, this enchanting corner-lot home is a perfect haven. The backyard oasis, fully enclosed with PVC fencing, includes a spacious covered porch. Inside, vaulted ceilings and an expansive kitchen with modern appliances add to the allure. The garage offers laundry hookups and ample storage. Tiled flooring, ceiling fans, and a walk-in closet in the master bedroom enhance the interior. Recent updates include a new roof and a modernized HVAC system in 2022. Conveniently located near a golf course, restaurants, and shopping areas, this residence combines practicality with aesthetic appeal for refined living. Call for a showing today!!!
